===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|handful}}, {{m|enm|hondful}}, from {{inh|en|ang|handful|t=handful}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*handufullō}}, {{m|gem-pro|*handufulliz|t=handful}}, from {{der|en|gem-pro|*handuz|t=hand}} + {{m|gem-pro|*fullaz|t=full}}; equivalent to {{compound|en|hand|full|t2=fullness, plenty}} or {{af|en|hand|-ful|pos=noun}}. Cognate with {{cog|stq|Hondful||handful}}, {{cog|fy|hânfol||handful}}, {{cog|nl|handvol||handful}}, {{cog|de|Handvoll|t=handful}}, {{cog|da|håndfuld||handful}}, {{cog|sv|handfull||handful}}, {{cog|is|handfylli||handful}}.

